text: Helmut Geuking (born 16 January 1964) is a German politician who is a Member of the European Parliament for Germany, representing the Family Party of Germany. He sits with the European Conservatives and Reformists Group and is also a member of the European Christian Political Movement. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1964 births Category:MEPs for Germany 2019–2024
